      "description": "Whenever you attack, each opponent loses X life and you gain X life, where X is the number of attacking creatures. If Mishra, Claimed by Gix and a creature named Phyrexian Dragon Engine are attacking, and you both own and control them, exile them, then meld them into Mishra, Lost to Phyrexia. It enters the battlefield tapped 9/9 and attacking.\r\n<br>\r\n-------------\r\n<br>\r\n<br><b>Meld Partner:</b> <a href=\"https://www.tcgplayer.com/product/448706/magic-the-brothers-war-phyrexian-dragon-engine?xid=pi92ede322-67fa-436f-827e-ef7ee496ec2b&Language=English&page=1\"><b> Phyrexian Dragon Engine</b></a>\r\n<br>When Melded, it becomes the following:</em>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Mishra, Lost to Phyrexia</strong>\r\n<br>\r\nLegendary Artifact Creature — Phyrexian Artificer\r\n<br>Whenever Mishra, Lost to Phyrexia enters the battlefield or attacks, choose three —\r\n<br>• Target opponent discards two cards.\r\n<br>• Mishra deals 3 damage to any target.\r\n<br>• Destroy target artifact or planeswalker.\r\n<br>• Creatures you control gain menace and trample until end of turn.\r\n<br>• Creatures you don't control get -1/-1 until end of turn.\r\n<br>• Create two tapped Powerstone tokens.",
